#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budgets"
msgstr "Budžeti"

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is a budget?"
msgstr "Šta je budžet?"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A budget is a categorized list of expected income and expenses for a period."
msgstr ""
"Budžet je kategorizirana lista očekivanih prihoda i rashoda za određeni "
"period vremena."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:19
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Budget facility of &kappname; allows you to create annual budgets. "
#| "More than one Budget can be created for any year. You set monthly Budget "
#| "values against any Income or Expense categories that you have defined. "
#| "The values can be set in three ways, depending on the Period:"
msgid ""
"The Budget facility of &kmymoney; allows you to create annual budgets. More "
"than one Budget can be created for any year. You set monthly Budget values "
"against any Income or Expense categories that you have defined. The values "
"can be set in three ways, depending on the Period:"
msgstr ""
"&kappname; Budget vam omogućava da napravite godišnje budžete. Više od "
"jednog budžeta može biti napravljeno za bilo koju godinu. Postavljate "
"vrijednosti budžeta za sve Income(prihod) ili Expense(rashod) kategorije "
"koje ste definisali. Vrijednosti se mogu postaviti na tri načina, u "
"ovisnosti od perioda vremena:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:28 details-budgets.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "Mjesečno"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "(Default) specify a single value applied to every month in the Budget"
msgstr ""
"(unaprijed definisano) odredite jednu vrijednost koja će se primijeniti na "
"svaki mjesec u Budžetu"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:34 details-budgets.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Yearly"
msgstr "Godišnje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:35
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "specify a single value to divide evenly across each month in the Budget"
msgid "Specify a single value to divide evenly across each month in the Budget"
msgstr ""
"odredite jednu vrijednost koja će biti podijeljenna na svaki mjesec budžeta "
"podjednako"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:40 details-budgets.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "Pojedinačno"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:42
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "specify separate values for each month."
msgid "Specify separate values for each month."
msgstr "odredite različite vrijednosti za svaki mjesec."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used for income and expenses spread irregularly through the year."
msgstr ""
"Ovo se koristi za prihode i rashode koji su nepravilno raspoređeni tokom "
"godine."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:49
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; provides a number of reports which compare actual income and "
#| "expenses against the entered Budgets. These are described in more detail "
#| "in <link linkend=\"budget.details.reports\">another section</link>."
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; provides a number of reports which compare actual income and "
"expenses against the entered Budgets. These are described in more detail in "
"<link linkend=\"budget.details.reports\">another section</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; pruža razne izvještaje koji upoređuju stvarne prihode i rashode "
"sa unesenim budžetom. Detaljnije informacije možete naći u <link linkend="
"\"budget.details.reports\">drugom poglavlju</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your budgets"
msgstr "Vaši budžeti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:57
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can access your budgets by clicking the appropriate icon in the "
#| "navigation pane at the left hand side of your &kappname; window."
msgid ""
"You can access your budgets in the <guilabel>Budgets View</guilabel>, which "
"you can display by clicking the appropriate icon in the View Selector at the "
"left hand side of your &kmymoney; window."
msgstr ""
"Svojim budžetima možete pristupiti pomoću klika na odgovarajuću ikonu u "
"navigacijskom panelu na lijevoj strani &kappname; prozora."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:63
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are two major sections to the budget window. These are described in "
#| "more detail below. On the left, the main section displays the list of "
#| "budgets you have created. Above that are buttons for creating, renaming, "
#| "and deleting budgets. On the right, there are three sections. At the top "
#| "is the Accounts List. At the bottom is a display of the amounts assigned "
#| "to the budget for the category selected in the Accounts List above. "
#| "Between those two areas are some additional controls for managing the "
#| "budget."
msgid ""
"There are two major sections in the Budgets View. On the left, there is a "
"list of budgets you have created. Above that are buttons for creating, "
"renaming, and deleting budgets. On the right, there are three sections. At "
"the top is the Categories List. At the bottom is a display of the amounts "
"assigned to the budget selected on the left for the category selected in the "
"Categories List above. Between those two areas are some additional controls "
"for managing the budget."
msgstr ""
"Budžetni prozor ima dvije glavne sekcije. One su u nastavku detaljno "
"opisane. Na lijevoj strani glavna sekcija prikazuje listu svih budžeta koje "
"ste napravili. Iznad toga su dugmad za pravljenje, reimenovanje i brisanje "
"budžeta. Na desnoj strani se nalaze tri sekcije. Na vrhu je Accounts "
"List(lista računa). Na dnu je prikaz vrijednosti dodjeljenih budžetu za "
"odabranu kategoriju u listi računa iznad. Između te dvije sekcije se nalaze "
"neke dodatne kontrole za upravljanje budžetom."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing, creating, renaming, and deleting budgets"
msgstr "Pregled, pravljenje, reimenovanje i brisanje budžeta"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:73
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This section of the Budgets window displays the list of Budgets contained "
#| "in the current &kappname; file. If no Budget has yet been created the "
#| "list will be empty. The list of Budgets has two columns:"
msgid ""
"The left section of the Budgets View displays the list of Budgets contained "
"in the current &kmymoney; file. If no Budget has yet been created the list "
"will be empty. The list of Budgets has two columns:"
msgstr ""
"Ova sekcija Budgets prozora prikazuje listu budžeta koji se nalaze u "
"trenutnoj &kappname; datoteci. Ukoliko nijedan budžet nije napravljen, lista "
"će biti prazna. Lista budžeta ima dvije kolone:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:81 details-budgets.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name of the Budget"
msgstr "Ime budžeta"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Year"
msgstr "Godina"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Fiscal year of the Budget. Note that the starting month and day of the "
#| "fiscal year can be specified in the <link linkend=\"details.settings."
#| "general.global\">Configure &kappname; dialog.</link>"
msgid ""
"Fiscal year of the Budget. Note that the starting month and day of the "
"fiscal year can be specified in the <link linkend=\"details.settings.general."
"global\">Configure &kmymoney; dialog.</link> To change the fiscal year of a "
"Budget, double click the year."
msgstr ""
"Fiskalnu godinu budžeta. Primiejtite da početni mjesec i dan fiskalne godine "
"mogu biti specificirani u <link linkend=\"details.settings.general.global"
"\">Configure &kappname; dijalogu.</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:100
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Values from the selected Budget are displayed to the right. To select a "
#| "different Budget you can click on the Budget in the list. Alternatively, "
#| "when the list has focus, you can select a different Budget using the up "
#| "and down keys. If you have made changes to a Budget and then select a "
#| "different budget &kappname; will ask you whether you want to save or "
#| "discard the changes."
msgid ""
"Values from the selected Budget are displayed to the right. To select a "
"different Budget you can click the budget name in the list on the left. "
"Alternatively, when the list has focus, you can select a different Budget "
"using the &Up; and &Down; keys. If you have made changes to a Budget and "
"then select a different budget, &kmymoney; will ask you whether you want to "
"save or discard the changes."
msgstr ""
"Vrijednosti iz izabranog budžeta su prikazane na desnoj strani. Da biste "
"odabrali drugi budžet, kliknite na Budget u listi. Alternativno, kada je "
"lista fokusirana, možete koristiti tipke up i down(gore i dole). Ukoliko ste "
"napravili promjene za neki budžet i onda odabrali neki drugi budžet, "
"&kappname; će vas pitati da li želite da sačuvate ili odbacite promjene."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are three buttons above the list of Budgets."
msgstr "Tri dugmeta se nalaze iznad liste budžeta."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>New</term>"
msgstr "<term>New</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new, empty budget. The default name of a new budget is \"Budget &lt;"
"year&gt;\" where &lt;year&gt; is the current fiscal year."
msgstr ""
"Pravi nov, prazan budžet. Unaprijed definisano ime novog budžeta je \"Budget "
"&lt;year&gt;\" gdje je &lt;year&gt; trenutna fiskalna godina."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename"
msgstr "Preimenuj"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:126
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can also edit the name of a Budget by double-clicking on the name of "
#| "a Budget in the list."
msgid ""
"Edit the name of the selected Budget. You can also edit the name of a Budget "
"by double-clicking the name of a Budget in the list."
msgstr "Ime budžeta možete promijeniti i dvostrukim klikom na budžet u listi."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Obriši"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:136 details-budgets.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the selected Budget."
