#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy budget"
msgstr "Kopiraj budžet"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a copy of the selected Budget. The new Budget has the name \"Copy of "
"&lt;budget&gt;\", where &lt;budget&gt; is the name of the copied Budget."
msgstr ""
"Pravi kopiju odabranog budžeta. Novi budžet će biti nazvan \"Copy of &lt;"
"budget&gt;\" gdje je \"Copy of &lt;budget&gt;\" ime kopiranog budžeta."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Budget based on forecast"
msgstr "Budžet baziran na proračunu"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:181
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Fills in budget amounts based on data from &kappname;'s Forecast values. "
#| "See the section on <link linkend=\"details.forecast.define\">Forecasts</"
#| "link> for more information."
msgid ""
"Fills in budget amounts based on data from &kmymoney;'s Forecast values. See "
"the section on <link linkend=\"details.forecast.define\">Forecasts</link> "
"for more information."
msgstr ""
"Popunjava vrijednosti budžeta baziranne na podacima iz &kappname; "
"proračunskih vrijednosti. Pogledajte sekciju na <link linkend=\"details."
"forecast.define\">Proračun</link> za više informacija."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Categories List"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Accounts List displays the list of Income and Expense Categories. "
#| "(Remember, within &kappname;, categories are treated as a special type of "
#| "account.) As in other places in &kappname;, the list is organized in a "
#| "tree structure. The list can be expanded or collapsed to show or hide "
#| "Subcategories within a Category. The Accounts List has a number of "
#| "columns:"
msgid ""
"The Categories List displays the list of Income and Expense Accounts. "
"(Remember, within &kmymoney;, categories are treated as a special type of "
"account.) As in other places in &kmymoney;, the list is organized in a tree "
"structure. The list can be expanded or collapsed to show or hide "
"Subcategories within a Category. The Categories List has a number of columns:"
msgstr ""
"Lista računa prikazuje listu kategorija prihoda i rashoda. (Zapamtite, u "
"&kappname;, kategorije se tretiraju kao posebna vrsta računa.) Kao i na "
"drugim mjestima u &kappname;, lista je organizovana kao stablo(struktura). "
"Lista može biti proširena ili sužena kako bi se vidjele ili sakrile "
"podkategorije unutar kategorije. Lista računa ima nekoliko kolona:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Aside from the Name column, all other columns may be shown or hidden by "
"right-clicking any column header, and checking or unchecking the checkbox "
"next to the column name. For more details about the meaning of each column, "
"see the <link linkend=\"details.categories.view\">Categories View</link> "
"section. Only the columns specifically relevant to Budgets are listed below, "
"but all Category columns may be displayed."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account (Category) name"
msgstr "Ime računa(kategorije)"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Category Type (Income or Expense)"
msgstr "Vrsta kategorije(prihod ili rashod)"

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:225
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Total Balance"
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "Ukupni bilans"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:227
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Current balance of Account. This will be blank for Categories, unless the "
#| "Category is defined in a foreign currency. In this case, Total Balance "
#| "will show the value for the Category in its defined currency."
msgid ""
"Current balance of Account. This will be blank for Categories, unless the "
"Category is defined in a foreign currency. In this case, Balance will show "
"the value for the Category in its defined currency."
msgstr ""
"Trenutni bilans računa. Ovo će biti prazno za kategorije, osim ako je "
"kategorija definisana za stranu valutu. U tom slučaju, ukupni bilans će "
"prikazati vrijednosti kategorije u definisanoj valuti."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total Value"
msgstr "Ukupna vrijednost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Total yearly value in the Budget. If a Category has Subcategories and the "
"Category's list of Subcategories is collapsed the value displayed is the sum "
"of the values for the Category and all of its Subcategories. If a Category "
"is defined in a foreign currency, the Total Value will show the value in the "
"base currency."
msgstr ""
"Ukupna godišnja vrijednost u budžetu. Ukoliko kategorija ima podkategorije i "
"njena lista podkategorija je sakrivena, vrijednost prikazana je zbir svih "
"vrijednosti kategorije i svih njenih podkategorija. Ukoliko je kategorija "
"definisana za stranu valutu, ukupna vrijednost će biti prikazana u toj "
"valuti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the Categories List are several controls. The <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-gtk-floppy.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"<guibutton>Upd</guibutton> (Update) and <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-edit-undo.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> <guibutton>Res</guibutton> "
"(Reset) buttons are described further below. The <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-zoom-out.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guiicon> collapse and "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"icon-zoom-"
"in.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"expand buttons collapse or expand the entire Categories List."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:264
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Accounts List can be filtered in two ways. Checking the \"Hide unused "
#| "categories\" checkbox hides any Categories for which no value has been "
#| "assigned to the Category or any of its Subcategories. To the right of "
#| "this, is an unlabelled text box. Only categories which include whatever "
#| "is typed in this box are listed, but their parent categories are also "
#| "listed."
msgid ""
"The Categories List can be filtered in two ways. Checking the <guilabel>Hide "
"unused budget categories</guilabel> checkbox hides any Categories for which "
"no value has been assigned to the Category or any of its Subcategories in "
"the selected budget. To the right of this, is an unlabelled text box. Only "
"categories which include whatever is typed in this box are listed, but their "
"parent categories are also listed."
msgstr ""
"Lista računa može biti filtrirana na dva načina. Označavanjem \"Hide unused "
"categories\" polja, sve kategorije kojim nije dodijeljena neka vrijednost "
"ili ukoliko nekoj od njenih podkategorija nije dodijeljenja vrijednost će "
"biti sakrivene. Desno od toga se nalazi neoznačen prostor. Samo kategorije "
"koje uključuju ono što je napisano u tom prostoru su prikazane, uključujući "
"i njihove \"roditeljske\" kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:273
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Note that changing either the \"Hide unused budget categories\" or the "
#| "filter value is likely to change the list of Categories display. You may "
#| "need to re-expand the list to see all the Categories that should be "
#| "displayed with the current settings."
msgid ""
"Note that changing either the <guilabel>Hide unused budget categories</"
"guilabel> or the filter value is likely to change the list of Categories "
"displayed. You may need to re-expand the list to see all the Categories that "
"should be displayed with the current settings."
msgstr ""
"Primijetite da će promjena ili \"Sakrij nekorištene kategorije budžeta\" ili "
"filtera vrijednosti vjerovatno utjecati na listu prikazanih kategorija. "
"Možda ćete morati proširiti listu da biste vidjele sve kategorije koje bi "
"trebale biti prikazane sa trenutnim postavkama."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assignments"
msgstr "Dodjele"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:282
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Assignments area shows the values for the Category selected in the "
#| "Accounts List."
msgid ""
"The Assignments area shows the values for the Category selected in the "
"Categories List."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj prostor prikazuje vrijednosti kategorija selektiranih u listi računa."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Račun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:291
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Displays the name of the selected Category. If the Category is a "
#| "Subcategory, its full name is displayed in the Category:Subcategory "
#| "format."
msgid ""
"The name of the selected Category. If the Category is a Subcategory, its "
"full name is displayed in the Category:Subcategory format."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje ime selektirane kategorije. Ukoliko je kategorija podkategorija, "
"njeno puno ime je prikazano u kategoira:podkategorija formatu."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total"
msgstr "Ukupno"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:301
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Displays the total yearly value assigned to the Category"
msgid "The total yearly value assigned to the Category."
msgstr "Prikazuje ukupnu godišnju vrijednost dodijeljenu kategoriji."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include subaccounts"
msgstr "Uključi podračune"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is checked, then Reports show actual income or expenses in "
"Subcategories belonging to the Category against the Category instead of the "
"Subcategory."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko je ovo obilježeno, onda će izvještaji prikazati stvarni prihod i "
"rashod u podkategorijama koje pripadaju kategoriji naspram kategorije "
"umjesto podkategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a Subcategory has a value defined in the Budget, then the income and "
"expenses are shown against the Subcategory."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko podkategorija ima vrijednost definisanu u budžetu, onda su prihod i "
"rashod prikazani naspram podkategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:319
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the Category selected in the Accounts List has its Subcategories "
#| "collapsed, although its Total Value will show the sum of the Total Values "
#| "for all its Subcategories, the amounts in the Assignments area may still "
#| "show 0, unless this box has been checked or an amount has explicitly been "
#| "assigned to the Category."
msgid ""
"If the Category selected in the Categories List has its Subcategories "
"collapsed, although its Total Value will show the sum of the Total Values "
"for all its Subcategories, the amounts in the Assignments area may still "
"show 0, unless this box has been checked or an amount has explicitly been "
"assigned to the Category."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko kategorija odabrana u listi računa ima podkategorije koje su "
"sakrivene, iako će ukupna vrijednost prikazati zbir svih totalnih "
"vrijednosti svih njenih podkategorija, vrijednosti u prostoru za dodjelu "
"mogu idalje prikazivati 0, osim ako je ovo polje obilježeno ili ukoliko je "
"vrijednost eksplicitno dodjeljena kategoriji."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:327
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In general, for you will either check this box and assign values to the "
#| "Category and not to any of its Subcategories, or not check the box, and "
#| "assign values to the Subcategories but not the Category. If any "
#| "Subcategories have assigned amounts when this box is checked, then those "
#| "amounts are rolled up to the Category."
msgid ""
"In general, you will either check this box and assign values to the Category "
"and not to any of its Subcategories, or not check the box, and assign values "
"to the Subcategories but not the Category. If any Subcategories have "
"assigned amounts when this box is checked, then those amounts are rolled up "
"to the Category."
msgstr ""
"Općenito, ili ćete obilježiti ovo polje i dodjeliti vrijednosti kategoriji a "
"ne i njenim podkategorijama, ili necete obilježiti ovo polje i dodjelicete "
"vrijednosti podkategorijama ali ne i kategoriji. Ukoliko bilo koja "
"podkategorija ima dodjeljenu vrijednost kada je ovo polje obilježeno, onda "
"će ta vrijednost biti smještena u kategoriji."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear"
msgstr "Očisti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:340
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Clear button resets the budgeted category value or values to zero."
msgid ""
"Clicking this button resets the budgeted category value or values to zero."
msgstr ""
"Tipka očisti resetuje vrijednost ili vrijednosti kategorije budžeta na nulu."

#. Tag: term
#: details-budgets.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Period"
msgstr "Period"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:349
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Period radio buttons allow you to select the period for which the "
#| "value applies"
msgid ""
"This radio buttons allow you to select the period for which the value applies"
msgstr ""
"Period dugmad vam omogućavaju da odaberete period za koju će se vrijednost "
"primjeniti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A single value is entered, specifying the amount per month. This is the "
"default setting."
msgstr ""
"Jedna vrijednost se unosi, koja određuje mjesečnu vrijednost. Ovo je "
"unaprijed definisana postavka."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid "A single value is entered, specifying the amount per year."
msgstr "Jedna vrijednost se unosi, koja određuje mjesečnu vrijednost."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Values are specified for each Calendar month. This is used where expense or "
"income is spread irregularly through the year."
msgstr ""
"Vrijednosti se određuju za svaki kalendarski mjesec. ovo se koristi kada su "
"rashod ili prihod nepravilo raspoređeni tokom godine."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:382
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If a value is or values are already specified and the Period is changed "
#| "&kappname; will ask whether to use the current total yearly value to "
#| "assign the new values."
msgid ""
"If a value is or values are already specified and the Period is changed, "
"&kmymoney; will ask whether to use the current total yearly value to assign "
"the new values."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko je vrijednost, ili vrijednosti, već određena i period je promjenjen, "
"&kappname; će pitati da li treba da koristi trenutno ukupnu godišnju "
"vrijednosr da dodjeli nove vrijednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-budgets.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update and Revert"
msgstr "Ažuriranje i vraćanje u prijašnje stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:393
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When a Budget's values are first modified, the Update and Revert buttons "
#| "are enabled. Multiple changes can be made to the Budget. Pressing Update "
#| "will store the changes and disable the Update and Revert buttons."
msgid ""
"When a Budget's values are first modified, the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> "
"and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> buttons are enabled. Multiple changes can "
"be made to the Budget. Pressing <guibutton>Update</guibutton> will store the "
"changes and disable these buttons."
msgstr ""
"Kada se prvi put vrijednosti budžeta modifikuju, Update i Revert tipke če "
"biti omogućene. Višestruke promjene su mogu napraviti nad budžetom. "
"Pritiskom na Update, promjene će biti uskladištene i tipke Update i Revert "
"će biti onemogućene."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:400
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The &kappname; Save only saves changes that have been stored using the "
#| "Update button. Thus, if you have modified a Budget but not yet stored the "
#| "changes &kappname; Save will not affect the modified Budget and the "
#| "Update and Revert buttons remain enabled."
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button only saves changes that have been "
"stored using the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> button. Thus, if you have "
"modified a Budget but not yet stored the changes <guibutton>Save</guibutton> "
"button will not affect the modified Budget and the <guibutton>Update</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> buttons remain enabled."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; Snimi samo spašava vrijednosti koje su uskladištene tipkom "
"Ažuriraj. Zato, ukoliko ste modificirali budžet ali niste uskladištili "
"promjene, &kappname; Snimi neće utjecati na modificirani budžet i tipke "
"Ažuriraj i Vrati će i dalje biti omogućene."

#. Tag: para
#: details-budgets.docbook:408
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Revert undoes any changes made to a Budget since the last Update and "
#| "disables the Update and Revert buttons."
msgid ""
"Revert undoes any changes made to a Budget since the last Update and "
"disables the <guibutton>Update</guibutton> and <guibutton>Revert</guibutton> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"Vrati poništava sve promjene u budžetu od posljednjeg korištenja Ažuriraj "
"tipke i onemogućuje Ažuriraj i Vrati tipke."

